{
  "stem": "6966.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I didn't want to tell him what happened to his brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In case he does hear me, then he knows what happened to Barron Dinstof-- who owes me still a quarter bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I gave him 20 canteen cigarettes-- bad stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He said, give them to me, and I'll get some bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we'll share.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It never came as far as that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Well, that was Monowitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "From Monowitz to Gleiwitz-- and from Gleiwitz we got in the trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And now starts a five day journey.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Those trucks had too many men.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Every morning when it stopped, four or five men came out of the trucks every morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were-- they were dead-- choked or frozen to death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was my turn one morning to-- the trains went during the night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But during the day, they didn't pass through the towns-- could the population-- should not see what happened in those carriages.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So it stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And one of those mornings, it was my turn to go out of-- get out of the truck with a little [NON-ENGLISH]-- is an aluminum container-- to get some snow from between the rails-- because there was nothing to eat, nothing to drink.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So it was my turn to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I was bending down and shoveling with my spoon-- snow into it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then I saw a couple of Wellingtons next to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I looked up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It was an SS guard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he dragged me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, what are you doing, you pig?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shit, he said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Get up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I says, well, give us something to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's nothing else to eat but-- but-- but snow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, what eat?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, carry your comrades!",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
